'''巴林－以色列和平協議'''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.haaretz.com/amp/israel-news/full-text-declaration-of-peace-signed-by-israel-and-bahrain-1.9159301|title=FULL TEXT: Declaration of Peace Signed by Israel and Bahrain|date=September 15, 2020|website=Haaretz|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2020-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213174311/https://www.haaretz.com/amp/israel-news/full-text-declaration-of-peace-signed-by-israel-and-bahrain-1.9159301|dead-url=no}},</ref>，正式名称为《'''亚伯拉罕协议:宣布和平、合作和建设性外交和友好关系'''》<ref>{{cite web |title=READ: Full text of the Abraham Accords and agreements between Israel and the United Arab Emirates/Bahrain |publisher=CNN |date=September 15, 2020 |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/09/15/politics/israel-uae-abraham-accords-documents/index.html |access-date=2020-10-13 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115060225/https://edition.cnn.com/2020/09/15/politics/israel-uae-abraham-accords-documents/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是一项使巴林和以色列之间的外交和其他关系正常化的协议。川普总统于2020年9月11日宣布了这项协议。<ref>{{Cite web|url= https://www.startribune.com/bahrain-to-recognize-israel-as-uae-deal-set-to-be-signed/572383612/|title= Bahrain to recognize Israel as UAE deal set to be signed|date= September 11, 2020|website= Star Tribune|access-date= 2020-09-12|archive-date= 2020-09-11|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200911183115/https://www.startribune.com/bahrain-to-recognize-israel-as-uae-deal-set-to-be-signed/572383612/|dead-url= no}}</ref> 此前，美国、以色列和阿联酋于2020年8月13日发表联合声明，正式称为《'''亚伯拉罕协议'''》。<ref name="#1">{{cite news|title=Read the full statement by the US, Israel and UAE on normalizing Israel-UAE relations|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/08/13/middleeast/mideast-trump-full-statement-uae-israel-intl/index.html|publisher=CNN|date=August 13, 2020|access-date=September 15, 2020|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115060226/https://edition.cnn.com/2020/08/13/middleeast/mideast-trump-full-statement-uae-israel-intl/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>协议于2020年9月15日在华盛顿特区的白宫正式签署，<ref name="bbc1">{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-54168120 |title=Trump hails 'dawn of new Middle East' with UAE-Bahrain-Israel deals |website=BBC |date=September 15, 2020 |access-date=2020-10-13 |archive-date=2020-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915193318/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-54168120 |dead-url=no }}</ref>使巴林成为第四个承认以色列的阿拉伯国家，也是一个月内第二个承认以色列的阿拉伯国家。<ref>{{Cite web|url= https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-54124996|title= Trump announces 'peace deal' between Bahrain and Israel|date= September 11, 2020|publisher= BBC|access-date= 2020-10-13|archive-date= 2021-01-20|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210120053853/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-54124996|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url= https://www.timesofisrael.com/bahrain-to-establish-full-diplomatic-relations-with-israel-trump-announces/|title= Bahrain to establish full diplomatic relations with Israel, Trump announces|first= Jacob|last= Magid|date= September 11, 2020|website= Times of Israel|access-date= 2020-09-12|archive-date= 2020-09-11|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200911184147/https://www.timesofisrael.com/bahrain-to-establish-full-diplomatic-relations-with-israel-trump-announces/|dead-url= no}}</ref>{{efn|另外还有一份简短的声明，标题为“亚伯拉罕协议声明:由包括巴林在内的四方签署，阿联酋和以色列的同期协议包含以下声明”，“重申美国、以色列和阿拉伯联合酋长国于2020年8月13日签署的联合声明”(“亚伯拉罕协议”);<ref name="#1"/>}}

==背景==
{{see also|巴林－以色列關係}}
2005年，巴林放弃了对以色列的抵制，以换取与美国的自由贸易协定。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/bahrain-wont-have-to-abolish-israel-boycott-law-because-it-did-so-years-ago/|title=Bahrain won't have to abolish Israel boycott law — because it did so years ago|first=Raphael|last=Ahren|date=September 14, 2020|work=The Times of Israel|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216184955/https://www.timesofisrael.com/bahrain-wont-have-to-abolish-israel-boycott-law-because-it-did-so-years-ago/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年5月20日至21日，55个穆斯林国家和美国在沙特首都利雅得举行峰会，讨论根除全球恐怖主义的方法。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2017/05/riyadh-summit-discusses-ways-rooting-terrorism-170521132843998.html|title=Riyadh summit discusses ways of rooting out terrorism|website=Al-Jazeera|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807011420/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2017/05/riyadh-summit-discusses-ways-rooting-terrorism-170521132843998.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 沙特阿拉伯国王萨勒曼和包括巴林在内的逊尼派国家领导人讨论了伊朗在中东日益增长的影响力和活动。以色列没有被邀请参加峰会。

2017年9月，巴林国王[[哈迈德·本·伊萨·本·萨勒曼·阿勒哈利法|哈迈德·本·伊萨·本·萨勒曼·阿勒哈利法]]在洛杉矶[[西蒙·维森塔尔中心|西蒙·维森塔尔中心]]对犹太教教士马文·希尔发表演讲，谴责阿拉伯联盟抵制以色列，称尽管两国没有外交关系，但巴林公民有权访问以色列。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/bahrains-king-opposes-arab-boycott-of-israel-jewish-leader-says/|title=Bahrain's king opposes Arab boycott of Israel, Jewish leader says|first=Dov|last=Lieber|date=September 18, 2017|work=The Times of Israel|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111221208/https://www.timesofisrael.com/bahrains-king-opposes-arab-boycott-of-israel-jewish-leader-says/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年5月8日，沙特阿拉伯、阿联酋和巴林公开表示欢迎并支持美国退出[[伊朗核协议|伊朗核协议]]，称伊朗在中东地区进行破坏稳定的活动。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thenational.ae/world/mena/uae-saudi-arabia-and-bahrain-welcome-trump-s-exit-from-iran-nuclear-deal-1.728557|title=UAE, Saudi Arabia and Bahrain welcome Trump's exit from Iran nuclear deal|website=The National|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2018-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180509080313/https://www.thenational.ae/world/mena/uae-saudi-arabia-and-bahrain-welcome-trump-s-exit-from-iran-nuclear-deal-1.728557|dead-url=no}}</ref>以色列也支持美国退出。<ref>{{cite news |date=May 8, 2018 |author=Lahav Harkov |title=World reacts to Trump's dramatic decision to exit Iran deal |newspaper=The Jerusalem Post |url=https://m.jpost.com/Middle-East/LIVE-World-reacts-to-Trumps-Iran-deal-decision-554823/amp |access-date=May 8, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180510023513/https://m.jpost.com/Middle-East/LIVE-World-reacts-to-Trumps-Iran-deal-decision-554823/amp |archive-date=May 10, 2018}}</ref> 由于伊朗在该地区日益增长的影响力和参与，巴林支持以色列对伊朗的立场，并拉近了两国的关系。在2018年5月叙利亚以色列-伊朗事件中，巴林外交部长表示支持以色列的“自卫权利”。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/bahrain-backs-israeli-strikes-on-iranian-targets-in-syria/|title=Bahrain backs Israeli strikes on Iranian targets in Syria|first=Raphael|last=Ahren|date=May 10, 2018|website=The times of Israel|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207223434/https://www.timesofisrael.com/bahrain-backs-israeli-strikes-on-iranian-targets-in-syria/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

2019年2月13日至14日，巴林和以色列参加了在波兰华沙举行的安全会议，会上讨论了伊朗日益增长的影响力。随后，以色列和海湾国家的关系变得更加紧密。2019年6月25日至26日，巴林在麦纳麦举办了“和平到繁荣”研讨会，特朗普政府在会上介绍了特朗普和平计划的经济部分。巴勒斯坦权力机构拒绝了该计划，并在以色列未获邀请的情况下抵制了会议，尽管以色列记者获准报道会议的过程。<ref>{{Cite web|publisher=Arab centre DC|url=http://arabcenterdc.org/policy_analyses/the-manama-meeting-and-its-winners-and-losers/|title=The Manama Meeting and Its Winners and Losers|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728023709/http://arabcenterdc.org/policy_analyses/the-manama-meeting-and-its-winners-and-losers/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年7月，巴林外交部长哈立德·本·艾哈迈德·阿勒哈利法和以色列外长[[伊斯拉尔·卡茨|伊斯拉尔·卡茨]]在美国举行会晤。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/after-long-wait-some-israeli-news-outlets-okayed-to-cover-bahrain-summit/|title=After long wait, some Israeli news outlets okayed to cover Bahrain summit|last=Ahren|first=Raphael|website=www.timesofisrael.com|language=en-US|access-date=June 20, 2019|archive-date=2019-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190712054542/https://www.timesofisrael.com/after-long-wait-some-israeli-news-outlets-okayed-to-cover-bahrain-summit/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年10月，以色列官员达纳·本维尼蒂斯-加贝出席了在巴林[[麦纳麦|麦纳麦]]举行的“海上和航空安全工作组”。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/in-rare-formal-visit-israeli-official-attends-anti-iran-bahrain-conference/|title=In rare formal visit, Israeli official attends anti-Iran conference in Bahrain|website=The Times of Israel|date=October 21, 2019|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2020-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425081539/https://www.timesofisrael.com/in-rare-formal-visit-israeli-official-attends-anti-iran-bahrain-conference/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年12月，耶路撒冷首席拉比什洛莫·阿马尔访问巴林，参加一个跨宗教活动。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/jerusalem-chief-rabbi-visits-bahrain-for-interfaith-event/|title=Jerusalem chief rabbi visits Bahrain for interfaith event, meets king|website=The Times of Israel|date=December 10, 2019|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2020-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200109045101/https://www.timesofisrael.com/jerusalem-chief-rabbi-visits-bahrain-for-interfaith-event/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年8月13日，特朗普总统宣布阿联酋和以色列将根据[[以阿和平协议|以阿和平协议]]实现关系正常化。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/13/us/politics/trump-israel-united-arab-emirates-uae.html|title=Israel and United Arab Emirates Strike Major Diplomatic Agreement|first1=Peter|last1=Baker|first2=Isabel|last2=Kershner|first3=David D.|last3=Kirkpatrick|first4=Ronen|last4=Bergman|date=August 13, 2020|work=The NY Times|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813152005/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/13/us/politics/trump-israel-united-arab-emirates-uae.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>巴林称赞该协议，称它将有助于地区稳定与和平。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://wtop.com/middle-east/2020/08/the-latest-uae-confirms-deal-to-establish-ties-with-israel/|title=The Latest: US envoy: UAE-Israel deal 'huge win' for Trump|date=August 13, 2020|website=WTOP|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2020-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200822164434/https://wtop.com/middle-east/2020/08/the-latest-uae-confirms-deal-to-establish-ties-with-israel/|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，作为双方日益加强合作的标志，巴林和沙特阿拉伯允许来往以色列的飞机飞越上空，作为对该协议的支持。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jpost.com/middle-east/kushner-saudi-arabia-agreed-to-open-its-airspace-to-all-flights-from-israel-641705|title=Kushner: Saudi Arabia agreed to open its airspace to all flights from Israel|website=The Jerusalem Post|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126081358/https://www.jpost.com/middle-east/kushner-saudi-arabia-agreed-to-open-its-airspace-to-all-flights-from-israel-641705|dead-url=no}}</ref>

