阿拉伯国家虽然仍然支持巴勒斯坦人的权利，<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/09/arab-league-ministers-agree-condemn-uae-israel-deal-200909141524785.html|title=Arab League: Ministers agree not to condemn UAE-Israel deal|date=September 9, 2020|website=Al Jazeera|quote=The goal all our Arab countries seek, without exception, is to end the occupation and establish an independent Palestinian state on the 1967 borders with East Jerusalem as its capital,|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115060530/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/09/09/arab-league-ministers-agree-not-to-condemn-uae-israel-deal/|dead-url=no}}</ref>但也越来越愿意寻求与以色列建立各种关系。特朗普政府采取的“零敲碎打”的方式，充分利用了以色列和巴勒斯坦冲突无法达成解决方案的问题，争取以色列和其他阿拉伯国家关系正常化。<ref>{{cite news|title=Israel-UAE deal shows how the very notion of Middle East peace has shifted under Trump|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-israel-uae-middle-east-peace/2020/08/16/e245a358-defc-11ea-8051-d5f887d73381_story.html|work=The Washington Post|date=August 16, 2020|access-date=August 16, 2020|archive-date=2020-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200816214302/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-israel-uae-middle-east-peace/2020/08/16/e245a358-defc-11ea-8051-d5f887d73381_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年8月26日，国王哈迈德·本·伊萨·本·萨勒曼·阿勒哈利法告诉来访的美国国务卿迈克·蓬佩奥，他的国家致力于建立一个巴勒斯坦国，并驳回了华盛顿推动阿拉伯国家与以色列关系正常化的努力。<ref>{{cite news|title=Bahrain rejects US push to normalize relations with Israel|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/bahrain-rejects-push-normalise-relations-israel-200826143913425.html|work=Al Jazeera|date=August 26, 2020|accessdate=2020-10-13|archive-date=2020-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200909033926/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/bahrain-rejects-push-normalise-relations-israel-200826143913425.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 然而，2020年9月11日，巴林和以色列宣布同意建立全面外交关系。<ref>{{cite news|title=Bahrain establishing full diplomatic relations with Israel, Trump announces|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/bahrain-to-establish-full-diplomatic-relations-with-israel-trump-announces/#gs.fvk8xw|work=Times of Israel|date=September 11, 2020|accessdate=2020-09-12|archive-date=2020-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200911184147/https://www.timesofisrael.com/bahrain-to-establish-full-diplomatic-relations-with-israel-trump-announces/#gs.fvk8xw|dead-url=no}}</ref>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普在宣布这一消息的当天表示:“对于引发9/11事件的仇恨，没有比这更有力的回应了。”<ref>{{cite web|author1=Michael Crowley|author2=David M. Halbfinger|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/11/world/middleeast/bahrain-israel-trump.html|title=Bahrain Will Normalize Relations With Israel, in Deal Brokered by Trump|website=The New York Times|date=September 11, 2020|access-date=2020-10-13|archive-date=2021-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218121103/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/11/world/middleeast/bahrain-israel-trump.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==协议==
两国同意建立外交关系，<ref>{{Cite web|date=September 12, 2020|title=Joint Statement of the United States, the Kingdom of Bahrain, and the State of Israel|url=http://eg.usembassy.gov/joint-statement-of-the-united-states-the-kingdom-of-bahrainand-the-state-of-israel/|access-date=September 13, 2020|website=U.S. Embassy in Egypt|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200913014540/https://eg.usembassy.gov/joint-statement-of-the-united-states-the-kingdom-of-bahrainand-the-state-of-israel/|dead-url=no}}</ref>这是巴林与以色列关系全面正常化的第一步。尽管表示巴林慎重地接受以色列的合法性，但哈马德国王强调，“作为一种战略选择，根据两国解决方案和具有国际合法性的相关决议，有必要达成公正和全面的和平。”特朗普表示，两国将互派大使，在两国开设大使馆，并开始在技术、卫生和农业等领域开展合作。该协议还允许在[[特拉维夫|特拉维夫]]和麦纳麦之间建立航班。<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=September 12, 2020|title=Bahrain, Israel set to form official ties|url=https://www.arkansasonline.com/news/2020/sep/12/bahrain-israel-set-to-form-official-ties/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316214402/https://www.arkansasonline.com/news/2020/sep/12/bahrain-israel-set-to-form-official-ties/|archive-date=2021-03-16|access-date=September 13, 2020|website=Arkansas Democrat-Gazette|language=en}}</ref>2020年9月15日，协议签署仪式在白宫举行。<ref name="bbc1"/> 该声明承认两国的主权，并指出两国已同意在未来就大使馆和其他议题寻求协议。<ref>{{cite news |title=Abraham Accords: Full text |url=https://www.jpost.com/middle-east/full-text-of-the-declaration-of-peace-between-israel-and-bahrain-642422 |accessdate=September 15, 2020 |work=The Jerusalem Post |date=September 15, 2020 |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930100632/https://www.jpost.com/middle-east/full-text-of-the-declaration-of-peace-between-israel-and-bahrain-642422 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

